name: .VITALBANK
summary: Learn about .VITALBANK files and view a list of programs that open them.

windows.name: Open over 400 file formats with File Viewer Plus.Free Download

instructions: To open a VITALBANK file in Vital (cross-platform):
Select the sandwich menu located in Vital's center.
From the sandwich menu, select Import Bank.
Browse to and open your VITALBANK file.
The presets your VITALBANK file contains will then appear in Vital.
